title: Mythoklash - 1980-1984 EP [2013]
description:
Mashup remixes of popular american songs from 1980 and 1984

Tracks 01-11 = 1980 songs
Tracks 12-21 = 1982 songs
Source for track 11 chosen by Ronny Mack
Tracks 22-25 = bonus tracks

Arranged & mixed by Mythoklash

Artwork by Madame Gilles
www.madamegilles.com

Thanks to: Madame Gilles, Dennis Woodroff

Released by Neophile Records
